ses 42-44. </div><div class="t m7a9 x74 h2b y51c ff4 fs10 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">17. </div><div class="t me96 x6f h2b y51c ff4 fs10 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">What solemn declaration did the apostle make to those Jews </div><div class="t m1342 x71 h2b y814 ff4 fs10 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">who contradicted and blasphemed? Verses 45-47. </div><div class="t m7a9 x61 h2b y679 ff4 fs10 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">18. </div><div class="t m12af x66 h2b y679 ff4 fs10 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">How did the gentiles respond to the gospel message? Verses </div><div class="t mdb x71 h2b y3b5 ff4 fs10 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">48, 49. </div><div class="t m7a9 x61 h2b y3b7 ff4 fs10 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">19. </div><div class="t me7b x66 h2b y3b7 ff4 fs10 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">What opposition followed? Verses 50-52.x </div><div class="t m24a x1b h2b y12e2 ff4 fs10 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">( 19 1 </div></div><div class="pi" data-data='{"ctm":[1.000000,0.000000,0.000000,1.000000,0.000000,0.000000]}'></div></div>
